channel.description: I changed the cache link because I updated the cache, I zipped the file as your supposed to everything in the cache folder make sure your in root directory. I zipped it correctly. Extension is .zip, I uploaded it to dropbox. Copyied link to clipboard pasted in CacheDownloader.java removed everything ahead from .zip so link ends in .zip changed the signlink to read the zipped file name everything I done was correct. I don't understand why it's not working.
